title: Making a flex grp for next season
body: hey people of OCE. I am looking for flex players for  next season to push HIGH if you are keen add me in-game no toxic or snowflake types plz. must have discord and a working mic MUST also be gold+  and 18+ i wouldn't say we are going to be a team but just a grp of people that plays most nights and want to improve in team play :) thankyou for reading looking forward to the add Copy paste my name might be easier
